- If the pod still fails during startup, first check whether logs show `Using backend AttentionBackendEnum.TRITON_ATTN for vit attention` or whether the code path still selects `FLASH_ATTN`. If it still selects `FLASH_ATTN`, the source patch may not have been applied or the build cache may have reused an old vLLM wheel.
